
# vim-wizard

__THIS IS STILL UNDER DEVELOPMENT__  

This plugin provides to search and display information from arbitrary sources using `+popupwin` feature.  
It's like [unite.vim](https://github.com/Shougo/unite.vim), [vim-clap](https://github.com/liuchengxu/vim-clap), etc and inspired by those.  

## Usage

### :Wizard[!] [{argument}, ...]

## Requirements

* Vim must be compiled with `+popupwin` feature

